<h2>Here We Go Again</h2>


<p>OK, well I just did a post on how to use Android Intent Filters with Appcelerator, so why not the other side of the coin. This time you'll learn how you can <b><i>send</i></b> Intents instead of receiving them. With this powerful native functionality you'll be able to leverage existing apps on your Android device to do some of your heavy lifting, like sharing images, sending text, and a whole bunch of other things.</p>

